---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro'
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Request a Review - BenchTheBots" 
  description="Submit your AI tool for an independent, technical review by our team"
>
  <Nav />
  
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <header class="mb-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Request a Review</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 mb-6">
        We review AI tools with rigorous testing and honest analysis. No pay-to-play, no fluff—just real benchmarks and technical insights.
      </p>
      
      <div class="bg-brand/10 border border-brand/30 rounded-sm p-6 mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">What to Expect</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-300">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-brand mt-1">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Independent Testing:</strong> We test with real use cases, not marketing materials</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-brand mt-1">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Honest Ratings:</strong> Good and bad—we don't sugarcoat</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-brand mt-1">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Technical Depth:</strong> Performance metrics, edge cases, and comparison benchmarks</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-brand mt-1">✓</span>
            <span><strong>2-4 Week Timeline:</strong> Thorough testing takes time</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="bg-slate-900/40 border border-slate-800 rounded-sm p-8">
      <form 
        name="review-request"
        method="POST"
        action="/success"
        data-netlify="true"
        netlify-honeypot="bot-field"
        class="space-y-6"
      >
        <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="review-request" />
        <p class="hidden">
          <label>Don't fill this out if you're human: <input name="bot-field" /></label>
        </p>

        <!-- Company/Individual Info -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div>
            <label for="contact-name" class="block text-sm font-medium mb-2">
              Your Name <span class="text-red-400">*</span>
            </label>
            <input 
              type="text" 
              id="contact-name"
              name="contactName"
              required
              class="w-full px-4 py-2.5 bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-brand"
            />
          </div>

          <div>
            <label for="email" class="block text-sm font-medium mb-2">
              Email <span class="text-red-400">*</span>
            </label>
            <input 
              type="email" 
              id="email"
              name="email"
              required
              class="w-full px-4 py-2.5 bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-brand"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <label for="company" class="block text-sm font-medium mb-2">
            Company/Organization
          </label>
          <input 
            type="text" 
            id="company"
            name="company"
            class="w-full px-4 py-2.5 bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-brand"
          />
        </div>

        <!-- Tool Information -->
        <div class="border-t border-slate-800 pt-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4">About Your AI Tool</h3>
          
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div>
              <label for="tool-name" class="block text-sm font-medium mb-2">
                Tool Name <span class="text-red-400">*</span>
              </label>
              <input 
                type="text" 
                id="tool-name"
                name="toolName"
                required
                placeholder="e.g., MyAI Assistant"
                class="w-full px-4 py-2.5 bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-brand"
              />
            </div>

            <div>
              <label for="tool-url" class="block text-sm font-medium mb-2">
                Website URL <span class="text-red-400">*</span>
              </label>
              <input 
                type="url" 
                id="tool-url"
                name="toolUrl"
                required
                placeholder="https://yourtool.com"
                class="w-full px-4 py-2.5 bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-brand"
              />
            </div>

            <div>
              <label for="category" class="block text-sm font-medium mb-2">
                Category <span class="text-red-400">*</span>
              </label>
              <select 
                id="category"
                name="category"
                required
                class="w-full px-4 py-2.5 bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-brand"
              >
                <option value="">Select a category...</option>
                <option value="llm">LLM / Chatbot</option>
                <option value="code">Coding Assistant</option>
                <option value="image">Image Generation</option>
                <option value="video">Video Generation</option>
                <option value="audio">Audio / Voice</option>
                <option value="writing">Writing / Content</option>
                <option value="productivity">Productivity</option>
                <option value="data">Data / Analytics</option>
                <option value="api">API / Infrastructure</option>
                <option value="other">Other</option>
              </select>
            </div>

            <div>
              <label for="description" class="block text-sm font-medium mb-2">
                Brief Description <span class="text-red-400">*</span>
              </label>
              <textarea 
                id="description"
                name="description"
                required
                rows="4"
                placeholder="What does your tool do? What problem does it solve?"
                class="w-full px-4 py-2.5 bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-brand resize-none"
              ></textarea>
            </div>

            <div>
              <label for="unique-features" class="block text-sm font-medium mb-2">
                What Makes It Unique?
              </label>
              <textarea 
                id="unique-features"
                name="uniqueFeatures"
                rows="3"
                placeholder="What sets your tool apart from competitors?"
                class="w-full px-4 py-2.5 bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-brand resize-none"
              ></textarea>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Pricing & Access -->
        <div class="border-t border-slate-800 pt-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4">Pricing & Access</h3>
          
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div>
              <label for="pricing-model" class="block text-sm font-medium mb-2">
                Pricing Model <span class="text-red-400">*</span>
              </label>
              <select 
                id="pricing-model"
                name="pricingModel"
                required
                class="w-full px-4 py-2.5 bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-brand"
              >
                <option value="">Select pricing model...</option>
                <option value="free">Completely Free</option>
                <option value="freemium">Freemium (Free tier + Paid)</option>
                <option value="subscription">Subscription Only</option>
                <option value="pay-per-use">Pay-per-use / Credits</option>
                <option value="one-time">One-time Purchase</option>
                <option value="enterprise">Enterprise Only</option>
              </select>
            </div>

            <div>
              <label for="starting-price" class="block text-sm font-medium mb-2">
                Starting Price (if applicable)
              </label>
              <input 
                type="text" 
                id="starting-price"
                name="startingPrice"
                placeholder="e.g., $20/month, $0.002/token, Free"
                class="w-full px-4 py-2.5 bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-brand"
              />
            </div>

            <div>
              <label class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <input 
                  type="checkbox" 
                  name="canProvideAccess"
                  value="yes"
                  class="mt-1 w-4 h-4 bg-slate-900 border-slate-800 rounded focus:ring-brand"
                />
                <span class="text-sm text-slate-300">
                  We can provide review access (free trial, API credits, or demo account)
                </span>
              </label>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Additional Info -->
        <div class="border-t border-slate-800 pt-6">
          <label for="additional-info" class="block text-sm font-medium mb-2">
            Anything Else We Should Know?
          </label>
          <textarea 
            id="additional-info"
            name="additionalInfo"
            rows="4"
            placeholder="Beta features, specific use cases to test, timeline constraints, etc."
            class="w-full px-4 py-2.5 bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-brand resize-none"
          ></textarea>
        </div>

        <!-- Partnership Interest -->
        <div class="bg-slate-900/60 border border-slate-700 rounded-sm p-4">
          <label class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <input 
              type="checkbox" 
              name="partnershipInterest"
              value="yes"
              class="mt-1 w-4 h-4 bg-slate-900 border-slate-800 rounded focus:ring-brand"
            />
            <div class="text-sm">
              <span class="text-slate-200 font-medium">Interested in partnership opportunities?</span>
              <p class="text-slate-400 mt-1">
                We occasionally work with companies on sponsored content, affiliate programs, or co-marketing. Check this if you'd like to discuss.
              </p>
            </div>
          </label>
        </div>

        <!-- Submit Button -->
        <div class="pt-4">
          <button 
            type="submit"
            class="w-full md:w-auto px-8 py-3 bg-brand hover:bg-brand/80 rounded-sm font-semibold transition-colors"
          >
            Submit Review Request
          </button>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-3">
            We review all submissions but can't guarantee coverage. We prioritize tools with unique value propositions and strong technical merit.
          </p>
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <div class="mt-12 space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <details class="bg-slate-900/40 border border-slate-800 rounded-sm p-5">
          <summary class="font-semibold cursor-pointer">Do you charge for reviews?</summary>
          <p class="text-slate-300 mt-3 text-sm">
            No. Our reviews are independent and unbiased. We don't accept payment for reviews or ratings. 
            We may use affiliate links in reviews, but this doesn't influence our testing or scores.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details class="bg-slate-900/40 border border-slate-800 rounded-sm p-5">
          <summary class="font-semibold cursor-pointer">How long does a review take?</summary>
          <p class="text-slate-300 mt-3 text-sm">
            Typically 2-4 weeks from receiving access. We do thorough testing across multiple use cases, 
            edge cases, and comparison benchmarks. Rush reviews aren't our thing.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details class="bg-slate-900/40 border border-slate-800 rounded-sm p-5">
          <summary class="font-semibold cursor-pointer">Can I see the review before it's published?</summary>
          <p class="text-slate-300 mt-3 text-sm">
            We'll fact-check technical details with you, but we don't offer editorial approval. 
            Our reviews reflect our honest testing and opinions.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details class="bg-slate-900/40 border border-slate-800 rounded-sm p-5">
          <summary class="font-semibold cursor-pointer">What if we get a bad review?</summary>
          <p class="text-slate-300 mt-3 text-sm">
            We're fair but honest. If there are issues, we document them with specifics. 
            Many tools have both strengths and weaknesses—that's normal. We also update reviews 
            as tools improve.
          </p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  details summary {
    list-style: none;
  }
  details summary::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }
  details summary::before {
    content: '›';
    display: inline-block;
    margin-right: 0.5rem;
    transition: transform 0.2s;
  }
  details[open] summary::before {
    transform: rotate(90deg);
  }
</style>
